=== RPCs ===
submit_form_v1(p_slug, p_form_type, p_payload) -- version 4
  Now persists draft_deals_id on intake_submissions row (1:1 link)
  All other logic unchanged from 10.12C

create_deal_from_intake_v1(p_fields jsonb)
  authenticated only, member+, write-lock enforced
  Creates real deals row with stage=new
  Atomic: deals + deal_inputs + deal_properties when supplied
  MAO derived server-side via _intake_apply_mao_to_assumptions_v1
  Field allowlist enforced -- unknown keys → VALIDATION_ERROR

promote_draft_deal_v1(p_draft_id uuid, p_fields jsonb)
  authenticated only, member+, write-lock enforced
  Promotes draft_deals row to real deals row with stage=new
  Merges draft fields with reviewed intake-user supplied fields (p_fields overlays)
  Marks intake_submissions.reviewed_at = now()
  Duplicate promotion rejected via CONFLICT (promoted_deal_id guard)
  Cross-tenant draft → NOT_FOUND
  Atomic: deals + deal_inputs + deal_properties when supplied

